Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.26,0:00:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的命運究竟是否在由看不見的力量或法則來掌控？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像神之手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  至少有一點很明確
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的自由不受任何意志的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王之卵!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常瞭解這個情景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差點就把Griffith給害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有聽說Hawks的事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在上次戰爭中失去了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知很確定  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部隊說他們在Chuder's 城堡裡遇到了一個巨大的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個巨大的惡魔?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣佈那不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們失敗的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連小孩玩花招都不如!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而Griffith成功地將城堡保護了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們也損失了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還聽說Griffith會被升級為貴族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的勝利使他在國王前的威望直線上升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好煩人!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王為什麼把這個頭銜給一個僱傭兵?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹之團的首領
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在戰場時有過不好的經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你在戰場上遇到過惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是不是那個惡魔傷了你?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你在黑暗中看到了一隻狗  還以為他是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我現在腿上負傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用你的血來祭我的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們全在這
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能走路嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人在責怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caska只是說因為那很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  你們現在去幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想去拜訪Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經有客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大臣和主教們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界有點殘忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些老臣們鄙視Griffith 而且說他是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新來的僱傭兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人卻討好他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們只是在幫他忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但Griffith至今仍然制無不勝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是Midland's最強軍隊的指揮官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有在聽我說  對不?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴過你在這等直到Griffith見客完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點關係都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想去見見負傷的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能進去的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等到會議結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ricket,你會跟我來嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼一直這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼Griffith對你如此器重?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那全部都弄糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一會兒回來!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點理解Guts的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後Griffith還是無法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像個陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該在那被Griffith給宰了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對你的手下一點都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像一條瘋狗!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼一直這樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是你的錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是你的錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經在邊緣上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來可以拿起你的劍了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管你被整得比我還慘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對昨天的事情道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說所有人都來看望我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我受傷的時候佔便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些大臣們有意識的每天都來訪問我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  他們很煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我別無它擇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nosferatu  Zodd
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡然有那麼龐大的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇見它就像在做惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有證明說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龐大的東西是存在的  儘管是在人類認知之上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可能是個上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它更像個惡魔  不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我是怎麼脫險的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在戰鬥中暈過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為在我脖子上的那個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你和那個人是真正的朋友的話  記好這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個人的野心成長時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就會死!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死是不可逃避的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zodd見過我帶的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這看起來像是在保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去謝謝那位預言者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又欠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴我你不想失去一個優秀的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一名為你而戰的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你差點就為了我而失去了你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我只是一個普通的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不應該發生在你這個想出人投地的人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我們3年前就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道理由嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想要為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次我決定用我的生命來保護你?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦白鷹先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的陛下!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼能在陛下的面前這樣!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  把頭抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是呼吸一下空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我的陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都很興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那些戰爭的商討
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alas,我想我不該再一次鎮定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我介紹你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的弟弟the  Earl  of  Yurius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是白龍的司令  而且是將來王冠的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Griffith,很榮欣見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你帶領Hawks勝利而驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很榮欣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在戰場上的表現使我忘了我的年齡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓我想上戰場!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起來我年輕時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我在殺場上的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  你不該這樣跟一個指揮官說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實該講
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些老的議員對你的存在很不滿意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你的影響而感到危機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們覺的你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會影響到midland的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  士氣和狀態不能夠給我們勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很關心我的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們生活在一個動亂的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我非常需要像你這樣的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像那些司令們一直以舊的規則辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓要把我的地盤發展強壯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你很期盼  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位小姐是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的女兒Charlotte
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她對戰士們很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她幾乎從不走出這城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個很內向的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太寵我這個唯一的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒她Griffith大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來Charlotte
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡然敢碰公主的身體!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  老頭子!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高貴的Yurius
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒什麼  父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得走了  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的需要一個原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次當我為你而死時?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說"為你"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道這到底是不是我想要的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用我的劍來為他戰鬥!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  所有人!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道這個要塞有多重要嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們應該知道你們的歷史!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著  因為我們佔領了Doldrey,我們可以第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的將敵人分開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  這個要塞是為軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻打midland而做準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著這條路!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條在Doldrey和Kingdom's  territory之間的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有很高的軍事價值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  我們的軍隊佔領了這條橋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭的趨勢改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣迫使他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Midland的心臟地帶暴露在我們眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個機密戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在Coborlwitz家庭流傳了300年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到勝利 就要佔領道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要勝利  我們的防守必須更強壯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的防禦已經計劃好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果敵人攻打我們的話  他們就得過這條橋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以Garrison裡的最好戰士會守在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個狹窄的石橋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能2人同時攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有Chuder最好的箭手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會站在大門上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的箭手會將在敵人一個一個過橋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們全部幹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會將敵人打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了我這個超級的設想  我們不應該有損失!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以放心了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果敵人不從橋這攻擊我們  而繞路到我們的後面怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這方圓8英里以內沒有一個橋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  這河很急  就連最好的馬都過不去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果敵人作木筏怎麼辦  還有..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所見 我們身處石地荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有那麼多樹來讓他們做木筏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他們做了足夠的木筏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一次也不能送足夠的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非他們能用籐條做出船來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼Griffith一康復我們就得出擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在戰場裡依靠我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他們不是說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管最厲害的騎士出擊  也無法將城堡擊破
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說他們受了很大的挫傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說2/3的騎士在橋上被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你是說真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪到我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會將他們殺的片甲不留
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個男人都會為自己的野心而付出性命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是當他們年輕的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們無法控制自己火焰燃燒般的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去得到輝煌  去失去夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些可以逃避命運的人們
